00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:04,050
Donraku child

97
00:06:04,050 --> 00:06:05,590
...has commitment issues and previously
 acknowledged affairs in the past.

98
00:06:04,050 --> 00:06:05,590
...influential rakugo storyteller Master Shofutei Donraku.

99
00:06:05,590 --> 00:06:06,590
